OL,3,CHow will no-jury trials work in
OL,4,CEngland and Wales?
OL,6,FPlans to scrap jury trials in England
OL,7,Fand Wales for cases for all but the
OL,8,Fmost serious offences have been set
OL,9,Fout by the government.
OL,11,FThe justice secretary announced a
OL,12,Fseries of "once in a generation"
OL,13,Freforms, including introducing "swift
OL,14,Fcourts", in a bid to tackle the record-
OL,15,Fhigh backlog of crown court cases,
OL,16,Fwhich has more than doubled in the
OL,17,Fpast six years.
