OL,3,CHow will no-jury trials work in
OL,4,CEngland and Wales?
OL,6,FDavid Lammy told the Commons on
OL,7,FTuesday he wants to "deliver the
OL,8,Fswifter justice victims deserve" as
OL,9,Fthe crown courts face a 78,000-strong
OL,10,Fbacklog.
OL,12,FA growing number of victims are giving
OL,13,Fup on seeking justice due to waiting
OL,14,Fyears for cases to make it to trial,
OL,15,Fwith some listed as far as ahead as
OL,16,F2030.
