OL,3,CHow will no-jury trials work in
OL,4,CEngland and Wales?
OL,6,FTaking a swipe at the previous
OL,7,FConservative administration, Lammy
OL,8,Ftold the Commons the government
OL,9,F"inherited an emergency in our
OL,10,Fcourts", adding: "This is a problem
OL,11,Fthat has taken years to build up, it
OL,12,Fwill take years to fix."
OL,14,FThe reforms are being introduced
OL,15,Ffollowing recommendations from a
OL,16,Freview by Sir Brian Leveson published
OL,17,Fearlier this year - but some experts,
OL,18,Fsuch as the Bar Council, argue
OL,19,Freplacing juries with single judges
OL,20,Fcould damage public trust.
