OL,3,CHow will no-jury trials work in
OL,4,CEngland and Wales?
OL,6,FHow will it work?
OL,8,FThe government will introduce new
OL,9,F"swift courts" where cases that likely
OL,10,Fcarry a sentence of three years or
OL,11,Fless will be heard by a lone judge.
OL,13,FParticularly technical and lengthy
OL,14,Ffraud and financial offence cases will
OL,15,Falso be tried by a single judge. The
OL,16,Fgovernment said this will free up
OL,17,Fjurors who usually have to give up
OL,18,Fmonths of their lives to hear
OL,19,F"particularly burdensome" cases.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
