OL,3,CHow will no-jury trials work in
OL,4,CEngland and Wales?
OL,6,FMagistrates will be given the power to
OL,7,Fhand down sentences of up to 18 months
OL,8,F- or two years if necessary -
OL,9,Fincreased from 12 months.
OL,11,FIt is hoped this will allow more cases
OL,12,Fto be heard by magistrates to free up
OL,13,Fcrown courts to deal with only the
OL,14,Fmost serious offences.
