OL,3,CHow will no-jury trials work in
OL,4,CEngland and Wales?
OL,6,FIn 2020, Lammy himself said scrapping
OL,7,Fjury trials during Covid would "damage
OL,8,Fdemocracy" because they are
OL,9,F"fundamental" to justice.
OL,11,FKeir Monteith KC, of Garden Court
OL,12,FChambers, told ITV News: "It doesn't
OL,13,Fmake sense. There's no logical reason
OL,14,Ffor him to do this.
OL,16,F"He was a proponent of the jury system
OL,17,Fbecause he had a belief that having
OL,18,Fjudges in charge would cause problems
OL,19,Fin relation to racism, institutional
OL,20,Fracism and bias."
